<!-- FORMAT -->
<section id="format" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
  <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">The Format</p>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What SHABBAT.md looks like</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-500 mb-10 max-w-2xl">
    Place a <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-mono text-gray-800">SHABBAT.md</code> file
    at the root of your repository. Any Shabbat-aware agent reads it to determine
    what it may and may not do — and when.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 mb-3">Full example</p>
      <div class="code-block">
        <div class="code-label">
          <span>SHABBAT.md</span>
        </div>
        <pre><span class="comment"># SHABBAT.md</span>

<span class="section">## Agent Identity</span>
<span class="key">- identity_type:</span> <span class="value-string">service-account</span>
<span class="key">- credentials:</span> <span class="value-string">dedicated</span>

<span class="section">## Shabbat Schedule</span>
<span class="key">- timezone:</span> <span class="value-string">America/New_York</span>
<span class="key">- pause_trigger:</span> <span class="value-string">shkia</span>
<span class="key">- resume_trigger:</span> <span class="value-string">havdalah</span>
<span class="key">- observe_yom_tov:</span> <span class="value-bool">true</span>

<span class="section">## Permitted Actions</span>
<span class="key">- read</span>       <span class="comment"># queries, browse, fetch</span>
<span class="key">- summarize</span>  <span class="comment"># synthesis of existing data</span>
<span class="key">- monitor</span>    <span class="comment"># watch and log, no alerting</span>

<span class="section">## Forbidden Actions</span>
<span class="key">- write</span>       <span class="comment"># disk, DB, external systems</span>
<span class="key">- deploy</span>      <span class="comment"># infra, releases (Boneh)</span>
<span class="key">- delete</span>      <span class="comment"># files, records (Mochek)</span>
<span class="key">- communicate</span> <span class="comment"># email, Slack, SMS as user</span>
<span class="key">- transact</span>    <span class="comment"># billing, payments (Mekach)</span>
<span class="key">- commit</span>      <span class="comment"># git commits (Kotev)</span>

<span class="section">## Human-in-the-Loop</span>
<span class="key">- pause_hitl_on_shabbat:</span> <span class="value-bool">true</span>

<span class="section">## Pikuach Nefesh</span>
<span class="key">- life_safety_override:</span> <span class="value-bool">false</span>

<span class="section">## Havdalah Audit</span>
<span class="key">- audit_enabled:</span> <span class="value-bool">true</span>
<span class="key">- format:</span> <span class="value-string">activity-log</span></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 mb-3">Minimal (MUTAR-safe defaults)</p>
